{"tid":1667034,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［1021］屯元天點搞？","createTime":"2019-10-21T08:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:24:25.000Z","uid":427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"878f754a87effc79b2183a68928d39102ad12cd9","tid":1667034,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"元朗重狗Yoho黨鐘收晒<br />\n屯元天各搞各？"},{"pid":"291003973b9b373a3913c88e238307ea386dcd82","tid":1667034,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d3d86e9d0ff5ff01d0178dacdfb1d5b2afe4fc9","tid":1667034,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ae22326357aa82a40b25579dde8f701e83f8df","tid":1667034,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:51:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12d17596e04fd6faad884a3ebf6eaa496905470f","tid":1667034,"uid":217542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:51:37.000Z","msg":"[突發] 北角好似有手足出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推 冇媒體報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43814272affbfeafa626a26546caa06f7403005f","tid":1667034,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"2d1c7abdd4282608996820c2de927f01fbe2fceb","tid":1667034,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"屯門牛最壞情況係入咗元朗之後 隨時cut埋輕鐵 要喺元朗搭巴士出市區 再搭巴士返屯門 然後大欖隧道同屯門公路轉車站又有rb"},{"pid":"32a610cecbfb16a80fa84a4e646303fb6e87a5aa","tid":1667034,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:57:07.000Z","msg":"轉場去屯門？"},{"pid":"6b9a825244b5a52cd623a80c3b98a6056938d6d9","tid":1667034,"uid":215066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得各搞各好D, 18區又可以做死狗"},{"pid":"d6f4a0f61c18ab850c9e27a510d78d031bf3fa7d","tid":1667034,"uid":257705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"TG Group 講緊七點大馬路集合"},{"pid":"ee849811456a4b0a5aba83c3585248efba912ea6","tid":1667034,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"878f754a87effc79b2183a68928d39102ad12cd9","tid":1667034,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"元朗重狗Yoho黨鐘收晒<br />\n屯元天各搞各？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"好似要行路去<br />\n不論狗定手足都set rb"},{"pid":"0685a90e69934d0dcf7dc6271ae4b8a84b3f442d","tid":1667034,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bdb12e98f4e890b21c2d5ec6f9d3fa4cf926af3","tid":1667034,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f4a0f61c18ab850c9e27a510d78d031bf3fa7d","tid":1667034,"uid":257705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"T